  "remarks": "Father’s name is Sheikh Ibrahim Ali Kaskar, mother’s name is Amina Bi, wife’s\nname is Mehjabeen Shaikh. International arrest warrant issued by the Government of India. Review\npursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 20 May\n2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
